## Classification Key

A ‚Äî Active authoritative: keep, server is source of truth
B ‚Äî Active legacy compatibility: still referenced, migrate away before removing
C ‚Äî Redundant but referenced: do not delete; update references first
D ‚Äî Unreferenced but risky: no client refs, but may be in trigger/policy/RPC bodies
E ‚Äî Safe removal candidate: no references anywhere

